    "category": "Data Interpretation",
    "explanation": "Real-world table problems combine data interpretation with practical applications. These include timetables, price lists, survey results, weather data, and sports statistics. Key skills: extracting relevant information, performing calculations, making comparisons, and drawing conclusions from complex data sets.",
